org.openstack4j.model.senlin

Interface Policy

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ModelEntity, ResourceEntity, Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    SenlinPolicy

    public interface Policy
extends ResourceEntity
    This interface describes the getter-methods (and thus components) of a Policy. All getters map to the possible return values of GET /v1/policies/​{policy_id}​
    Author:
    lion
    See Also:
    http://developer.openstack.org/api-ref-clustering-v1.html
